fields.name: Blackleg Injection
fields.description: Black Leg is for the active immunisation of cattle against diseases caused by Cl. chauvoei, Cl. septicum, Cl. novyi and Cl. tetani. A serological response to Cl. haemolyticum is induced in susceptible cattle, but efficacy of this component has not been demonstrated in cattle. It is applied at 2ml per animal.

fields.name: JFC Gate/Fence Feeder - Single
fields.description: JFC Gate/Fence Feeder - Single is suitable for cattle, sheep, horses, pigs and goats. JFC Gate/Fence Feeder - Single is manufactured from medium density polyethylene which is extremely tough and durable and offers strong resistance to severe impact. The rounded edge design ensures animal safety. The design includes 4 reinforced hangers for easy mounting on a fence, gate or rail and it comes fitted with 2 plastic hooks to provide extra stability and prevent the animal from knocking the feeder JFC Gate/Fence Feeder - Single is suitable for indoor or outdoor use and each feeder has a smooth, seamless finish which helps reduce feed build up and makes cleaning simple.

fields.name: Lamb Tag Applicator
fields.description: TheLamb tag Applicatoris a manual tag applicator used for applying tags on lambs. It is easy to use and reloads in seconds. Tagging at birth is recommended by the department.
